personalInfo.splInterest: Working out, Ultimate Fighting Championship, NFL, NBA

tourBios.carHigh: Has missed the cut in all three career starts on the Nationwide Tour, including The Rex Hospital Open and the Chattanooga Classic in 2010. Only PGA TOUR start came as an amateur at the 2008 U.S. Bank Championship in Milwaukee, where he missed the cut.
tourBios.otherCarHigh: Won five collegiate events while at the University of Wisconsin. All-American selection in 2007.
tourBios.personal: Favortie course is Southern Hills CC in Tulsa, OK. Would like to play Augusta National. Favorite teams are the Wisconsin Badgers and the Green Bay Packers. Favorite TV show is "Entourage," and "Tin Cup" is his favorite movie. Pizza is his favorite food. Tiger Woods and Kobe Bryant are his favorite athletes to watch. Enjoys a vacation anywhere there is a beach...Would round out his dream foursome with his father and a couple of buddies.
tourBios.otherInfo: Has played on the eGolf and Hooters Tours.

dyn.dynResults: His best finish on the Web.com Tour was T18th in 2011 at the WNB Golf Classic.
